{"id":109544,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/国家疟防所周水森主任妙释nsa项目/","date":"2010-09-28T23:42:01Z","modified":"2010-09-28T23:42:01Z","title":"国家疟防所周水森主任妙释NSA项目","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><b><span>HPA</span></b></span><b><span>东亚讯  </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span>日</span><span>，国家疟防所主任周水森老师受邀为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>HPA</span></span><span>举行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>NSA</span></span><span>培训会议。会议由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>HPA</span></span><span>云南代表处张军主任主持。周水森老师重点进行了全球基金项目的介绍、项目管理要求、中国消除疟疾计划和全球基金中国国家策略申请（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>NSA</span></span><span>）介绍。</span></p>\n<p><div><span><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=330\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241942091hrr1.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a></span></div>\n<div><span><b>周水森老师在讲座上</b></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><span>据悉，周水森老师曾担任第五轮中国全球基金疟疾项目办副主任，在疟疾防治项目有着丰富的管理经验和实践经验。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=331\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241943351Cx4O.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a><span><a href=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/batch.download.php?aid=332\"><img src=\"http://www.healthunlimited.org.cn/attachments/2010/08/24_201008241945491BJ1p.thumb.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a><br /><b><span>HPA员工认真听讲座</span></b></span><span></span></div>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span>周水森老师表示，在当前第十轮全球基金疟疾项目和中国消除疟疾计划的大别境下，跨境疟疾传播成为大问题，云南边境地区也成为重点关注的区域。因而，为了更好地开展</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>NSA</span></span><span>项目，周水森老师跟与会代表分享了球五的经验和教训，并重点介绍了项目管理的众多事项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><br /></span></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[1],"tags":[14483,8771]}